 "data": "@startuml
title Detailed Risk Score Calculation Process

start
:Initialize Risk Score = 0;

:For each company, evaluate the following criteria;

repeat
 :Training Completion Rates;
 if (Training given?) then (Yes)
 if (Completion > 80%) then (Yes)
 :Add 1 point;
 else
 if (50% <= Completion <= 80%) then (Yes)
 :Add 0.5 points;
 else (No)
 :Add 0 points;
 endif
 endif
 else (No)
 :Add 0 points;
 endif

 :Phishing Click Rates;
 if (Phishing done?) then (Yes)
 if (Click Rate < 5%) then (Yes)
 :Add 1 point;
 else
 if (5% <= Click Rate <= 10%) then (Yes)
 :Add 0.5 points;
 else (No)
 :Add 0 points;
 endif
 endif
 else (No)
 :Add 1 point; // No phishing results add full points
 endif

 :Critical Vulnerabilities;
 if (Count == 0) then (Yes)
 :Add 1 point;
 else
 if (Count <= 5) then (Yes)
 :Add 0.5 points;
 else (No)
 :Add 0 points;
 endif
 endif

 :High-Risk Vulnerabilities;
 if (Count == 0) then (Yes)
 :Add 1 point;
 else
 if (Count <= 5) then (Yes)
 :Add 0.5 points;
 else (No)
 :Add 0 points;
 endif
 endif

 :Medium-Risk Vulnerabilities;
 if (Count == 0) then (Yes)
 :Add 1 point;
 else
 if (Count <= 10) then (Yes)
 :Add 0.5 points;
 else (No)
 :Add 0 points;
 endif
 endif

 :Low-Risk Vulnerabilities;
 if (Count == 0) then (Yes)
 :Add 1 point;
 else
 if (Count <= 20) then (Yes)
 :Add 0.5 points;
 else (No)
 :Add 0 points;
 endif
 endif

 :Security Controls Audit Score;
 if (Audit conducted?) then (Yes)
 if (Score > 80) then (Yes)
 :Add 1 point;
 else
 if (Score >= 60) then (Yes)
 :Add 0.5 points;
 else (No)
 :Add 0 points;
 endif
 endif
 else (No)
 :Add 0 points; // No audit results add no points
 endif

repeat while (More Companies?)

:Determine Risk Level from Risk Score;
if (Score <= 2) then (Very High Risk)
 :Most Likely to Be Breached (Very High Risk);
else
 if (Score <= 4) then (High Risk)
 :Highly Vulnerable;
 else
 if (Score <= 6) then (Moderate Risk)
 :Moderately Vulnerable;
 else
 if (Score <= 8) then (Low Risk)
 :Minimally Vulnerable;
 else (Very Low Risk)
 :Least Likely to Be Breached (Very Low Risk);
 endif
 endif
 endif
endif

stop
@enduml
